FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780311775
OL,3,CWes Streeting backs North Sea oil
OL,4,Clicences and national insurance cut
OL,6,FWriting in The Observer, he said
OL,7,FLabour should be "cautious about
OL,8,Ftreating populism as a consequence
OL,9,Fsimply of economics" with Brexit and
OL,10,FDonald Trump showing "cultural
OL,11,Fquestions also matter".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FHe added: "Too often progressive
OL,19,Fpositions on these issues seem to have
OL,20,Fbeen driven by noisy pressure groups,
OL,21,Fnot common sense."
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@TO]rD@VOUsD@VO]zD@KOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
