PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780311775
OL,3,CWes Streeting backs North Sea oil
OL,4,Clicences and national insurance cut
OL,6,FBuilding on his earlier policy
OL,7,Fprescriptions, Sir Tony suggested the
OL,8,Fpublic would support a "rethinking of
OL,9,Fhealthcare", more flexible labour
OL,10,Fregulations, and cuts to welfare to
OL,11,Fpay for increased defence spending.
OL,13,FThe former prime minister also argued
OL,14,Fthat technology innovation is a "very
OL,15,Fopen competition in which Britain
OL,16,Fcould and must be well placed".
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@KO]vD@aOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
